INNER JOIN `Invoices` AS `c.Invoice` ON `c`.`InvoiceId` = `c.Invoice`.`Id`
WHERE (`c`.`UserId` = @__user_Id_0) AND (`c.Invoice`.`Invoice_Type` = 'Draft')
ORDER BY `c`.`Id` DESC" (0723d8ff)
